OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAshraf Ghani: Ex-Afghan    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpresident describes moment 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fhe fled the Taliban        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Afghanistan's former president has     
OL,6, defended his decision to flee the      
OL,7, country as the Taliban closed in       
OL,8, earlier this year, saying he did it to 
OL,9, prevent the destruction of Kabul.      
OL,11,FThe Taliban seized power in August     
OL,12,Fafter taking control of the capital.   
OL,14,FAshraf Ghani revealed that when he woke
OL,15,Fup on 15 August he had "no inkling" it 
OL,16,Fwould be his last day in Afghanistan.  
OL,18,FIt was only when his plane left Kabul  
OL,19,Fthat he realised he was going, Mr Ghani
OL,20,Fsaid on BBC Radio 4's Today programme. 
